promptTranslations.en:
Creative artistic typography for “纵有疾风起” (“Though the fierce wind rises”), with elegant handwritten style, text arranged horizontally, delivering strong visual impact;
Deeply integrates the free brush calligraphy style, brushstrokes showing the rough and uninhibited power of brush ink splashes;
Flying white (negative space) at stroke beginnings and ends, with pauses and accents, fully expressing promotional intensity; text shapes break regularity with varied stroke thickness;
Dutch angle composition creates dynamic sprinting momentum, letterforms exuberant and vigorous;
Raised center of gravity as if coiled to launch, brushstrokes extend freely and cross uninhibitedly, resembling full-speed dash force;
Structure is a woven mix of dense and sparse; dense parts like a surging promotional wave, white spaces like breathing gaps between offers;
Pure black background base perfectly matches the passionate atmosphere; text shape and color convey a powerful, unrestrained artistic style.
